\pard\sa80\f0\fs24 \b Summary\par
\pard\sa120\f0\fs18 Three IGC files held in IGCfiles/ were checked for conformance with the IGC flight-log format. \b All three pass\b0  \u8212? each is a complete, untruncated log carrying the mandatory header records, a full set of B (GPS fix) records, and a valid trailing security (G) record block with no data records after it.\par
